Gunmen suspected of being kidnappers have killed a soldier in Ondo State. The soldier was killed when the gunmen kidnapped a Lebanese engineer. The incident happened in Ogbonmo, Ijebu-Owo in Owo Local Government Area of Ondo State. It was gathered that the driver of the Lebanese was also killed in the attack. SP Fumilayo Odunlami, the police spokesperson in Ondo, confirmed the incident and said that efforts were being made to secure the victimâ€™s release.